Systemwide Environment Variables - Add in /etc/bashrc file    

These will be used by all the users system-wide without updating everytime.


export M2_HOME=/usr/local/apache-maven/apache-maven-3.5.4
export M2=$M2_HOME/bin
export JAVA_HOME=/usr/lib/jvm/jre-1.8.0-openjdk-1.8.0.171-8.b10.el7_5.x86_64
export PATH=$JAVA_HOME/bin:$M2:$PATH
